  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/549780/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765118995\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/549780/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765118995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/549780/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765118995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/549780/extras/fc743ba05187fd67cd8a6b5e064eb606.avif?t=1765118995\" width=600 height=118 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rage it up!!!!!!!!!!</h2><br>Rainbow Rage Squad is a platforming, wall jumping, saw dodging, game that includes 3 modes – Adventure, Time Attack, and Battle Mode. 40 levels full of insane obstacles, mayhem, and terrible level design as you make your way thru 4 total bosses....You will Rage!!!!!!  <br><br>Features<br><br>Up to 4 players Local<br>Local Co-Op<br>Time Trials<br>Battle Mode<br>40 Levels<br>Boss Fights<br>Unlockables<br>Rage, and Rainbows!!!!<br><br><br>GAMEPADS / CONTROLLERS RECOMMEND - This game is Designed for play with the Xbox 360 / Xbox One controller and some others do work. Keyboard is possible but not too enjoyable.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/549780/extras/fc743ba05187fd67cd8a6b5e064eb606.avif?t=1765118995\" width=600 height=118 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rage it up!!!!!!!!!!</h2><br>Rainbow Rage Squad is a platforming, wall jumping, saw dodging, game that includes 3 modes – Adventure, Time Attack, and Battle Mode. 40 levels full of insane obstacles, mayhem, and terrible level design as you make your way thru 4 total bosses....You will Rage!!!!!!  <br><br>Features<br><br>Up to 4 players Local<br>Local Co-Op<br>Time Trials<br>Battle Mode<br>40 Levels<br>Boss Fights<br>Unlockables<br>Rage, and Rainbows!!!!<br><br><br>GAMEPADS / CONTROLLERS RECOMMEND - This game is Designed for play with the Xbox 360 / Xbox One controller and some others do work. Keyboard is possible but not too enjoyable.",
